important
issues being dealt with by the
Senate Foreign

37:31.048 --> 37:32.984 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Relations Committee.

37:33.017 --> 37:38.322 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
