able to sell
it commercially.

51:58.782 --> 52:01.852 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They come in a huge variety of
colors.

52:01.885 --> 52:04.888 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You have parrot ones that have
the multiple
colors.

52:04.921 --> 52:05.956 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
