52:25.075 --> 52:29.346 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the way it's colored, it's
put in blue
water, and then it becomes a
beautiful blue.

52:29.379 --> 52:34.384 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Tulips, they are definitely the
springtime
flower that you see around.

52:34.417 --> 52:38.788 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I think it brings people
happiness.

